casebody.data:
Josephine WILLIAMS, Administratrix of the Estate of Tiffany Keyetta Jordan
v.
SCOTLAND COUNTY and the City of Laurinburg acting by and through Their employees and agents. No. 9P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 2, 2005. Jeffrey H. Blackwell, Wilmington, for City of Laurinburg. W. Edward Musselwhite, Jr., Lumberton, for Josephine Williams.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 7th day of January 2005 by Defendant (The City of Laurinburg) in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 2nd day of March 2005."
